  "body": "Hello! \r\nI picked up a local node and forked  `Polygon` across `Infura`.\r\nBlockchain requests and transactions take a very long time.\r\n* Ð¡alls on average 30 seconds.\r\n* Transactions from a minute to an error with a timeout. \r\n\r\nI do not know what this problem is related to. \r\nSometimes calls to the blockchain occur without delay, but most often there is a timeout .\r\nTried increase memory with command:  `--max-memory 8096` but it didn't speed up. \r\n\r\nI run it with the command:  `npx hardhat  node --max-memory 8096`\r\n\r\nVersions:\r\n```\r\nnode: v16\r\nhardhat: 2.6.8\r\nweb3: 1.5.2\r\nLinux: 5.15.3-arch1-1\r\n```\r\n",
